TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Identify SFDC records from DVT_Eligibility__c table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT /*+ PARALLEL(sf, 4) */ DISTINCT m.MEME_CK, g.GRGR_ID, g.GRGR_CK, a.SBAD_COUNTY, g.GRGR_STATE, e.MEPE_EFF_DT, e.MEPE_TERM_DT, e.MEPE_ELIG_IND, m.MEME_HICN, m.SBSB_CK, sf.SF_ID_ACCT, s.SBSB_ID, e.CSCS_ID, e.CSPI_ID, e.PDPD_ID, m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m inner join CMC_GRGR_GROUP g on m.grgr_ck = g.grgr_ck and substr(GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCD' inner join CMC_SBSB_SUBSC s on m.sbsb_ck = s.sbsb_ck inner join CMC_SBAD_ADDR a on m.sbsb_ck = a.sbsb_ck and M.SBAD_TYPE_HOME = A.SBAD_TYPE inner join CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e on m.meme_ck = e.meme_ck inner JOIN agp.SFDC_MEMBER sf on (g.GRGR_STATE||'MCD'||TRIM(m.MEME_MEDCD_NO)) = sf.MBR_EXT_ID WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT max(ex.MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG ex WHERE ex.meme_ck = E.meme_ck AND ex.MEPE_EFF_DT < sysdate) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM agp.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t WHERE m.meme_ck = t.caid_meme_ck AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT /*+ PARALLEL(sf, 4) */ DISTINCT m.MEME_CK, g.GRGR_ID, g.GRGR_CK, a.SBAD_COUNTY, g.GRGR_STATE, e.MEPE_EFF_DT, e.MEPE_TERM_DT, e.MEPE_ELIG_IND, m.MEME_HICN, m.SBSB_CK, sf.SF_ID_ACCT, s.SBSB_ID, e.CSCS_ID, e.CSPI_ID, e.PDPD_ID, m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m inner join CMC_GRGR_GROUP g on m.grgr_ck = g.grgr_ck and substr(GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCD' inner join CMC_SBSB_SUBSC s on m.sbsb_ck = s.sbsb_ck inner join CMC_SBAD_ADDR a on m.sbsb_ck = a.sbsb_ck and M.SBAD_TYPE_HOME = A.SBAD_TYPE inner join CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e on m.meme_ck = e.meme_ck inner JOIN agp.SFDC_MEMBER sf on (g.GRGR_STATE||'MCD'|| TRIM(m.MEME_MEDCD_NO)) = sf.MBR_EXT_ID --s.sbsb_id = substr(sf.member_external_id, 1,9) WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT max(ex.MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG ex WHERE ex.meme_ck = E.meme_ck AND ex.MEPE_EFF_DT < sysdate) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND round(to_char(months_between(trunc(sysdate),MEME_BIRTH_DT)/12), 2) >= 64.66
